==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Redraw
<hw>Re*draw"</hw> <pr>(r⟦emac⟧*dr⟦add⟧")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp.</pos> <conjf>Redrew</conjf>
<pr>(r⟦emac⟧*dr⟦udd⟧")</pr>;<pos>p. p.</pos> <conjf>Redrawn</conjf>
<pr>(r⟦emac⟧*dr⟦add⟧n")</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Redrawing</conjf>.]</vmorph> <def>To draw again; to make a second
