<p><ent>Redraw</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Redraw
<hw>Re*draw"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <fld>(Com.)</fld> <def>To draw a new
bill of exchange, as the holder of a protested bill, on the drawer or
indorsers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Redress</ent>⟦br⟧
